image_analysis.description: A photograph of a narrow, galley-style kitchen. The kitchen features white cabinetry, dark countertops, and light-colored hardwood flooring. On the left, there is a stainless steel sink, a range with a griddle, and a vent hood. On the right, a long counter with white cabinets underneath extends into the foreground, with a black lantern-style pendant light hanging above it. In the background, there is a smaller prep area with a sink, a water cooler, and more white cabinetry. Recessed lighting and a smoke detector are visible on the ceiling.
image_analysis.layout: Interior kitchen view, portrait orientation, looking down the length of the room.
